rting from `utils.ts` where it\'s already exported. Violates DRY.\n\n**Minor Iss
ues:**\n7. **UITweens inconsistency** - `UIToast.ts` uses hardcoded animation va
lues (`duration: 300`, `ease: \'Back.out\'`) instead of `UITweens.toastIn` / `UI
Tweens.toastOut`. Same for `UIAlert.ts`.\n8. **ToastManager monkey-patching** - 
