heck one more thing - does the UIPanel overlay properly block clicks to the scen
e? The overlay is a child of the panel container. In Phaser 3, container childre
n can be interactive and they do block events to objects beneath them (in the sa
me container or at lower depths). The overlay covers the whole screen. Since the
