being the last child checked in the container, only gets events if no other chil
d handled them. But for clicks outside the panel, no other child is under the cu
rsor, so the overlay gets the event and calls `onOverlayClick`. This correctly "
blocks" the click from reaching scene objects.\n\nActually, I should verify: doe
s Phaser\'s input system propagate events to lower-depth objects if a higher-dep
