ight not be imported in `UIToast`... actually `UIToast.ts` doesn\'t import `UIAl
ert`. Adding that import would create a dependency. It\'s not a big deal since t
hey\'re in the same layer, but it\'s also not necessary. I\'ll keep this as Mino
r.\n\nNow let me write the report. I\'ll also need to create the `logs/` directo
ry if it doesn\'t exist.',
